# Form Guidelines

## Core Principles

1. **Custom Implementation Required**
   - Do NOT use Nuxt Form components
   - Build forms using standard HTML and Tailwind CSS

2. **Formspree Integration**
   - All forms must include the following base structure:
   ```html
   <form
     action="https://formspree.io/f/mldgzjze"
     method="POST"
   >
     <!-- Form content here -->
   </form>
   ```

3. **Best Practices**
   - Use semantic HTML elements
   - Implement proper form validation
   - Include appropriate ARIA labels
   - Ensure responsive design
   - Add proper error handling



## Development Process
1. Start with basic HTML structure
2. Add Formspree integration
3. Style using custom CSS
4. Implement validation
5. Add error handling
6. Test thoroughly

